    "description": "《米诺利亚》（Minoria）是Bombservice的最新力作和最具雄心的游戏作品，也是该工作室《莫莫多拉》系列的精神续作。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/940910/extras/fc2d3b81c59662eabab226beb63d8521.poster.avif?t=1751610521\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/940910/extras/fc2d3b81c59662eabab226beb63d8521.webm?t=1751610521\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/940910/extras/fc2d3b81c59662eabab226beb63d8521.mp4?t=1751610521\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《莫莫多拉》的粉丝在逐渐掌握这款游戏招架、躲闪和各种技能的同时，也会在游戏设计和游戏过程中发现一些熟悉的元素。<br><br>本款游戏采用高清画面，背景为2D手绘风格，人物则为卡通渲染风格。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/940910/extras/1fdc664bafa8fa70afa709aee7f9c5f4.avif?t=1751610521\" width=594 height=118 /></span><br><strong>剧情</strong><br>故事发生在第四次女巫之乱期间，人们对于宗教高度狂热。只手遮天的圣部为了净化危及人类的罪人，领导裁判所严酷打击邪端异教。与此同时，背负“女巫”这一标签的人则正在举行一场有悖教会教规的神秘典礼。<br><br>跟随教会的两位教士赛弥拉修女和芙兰修女，踏上远征之徒，阻止女巫完成禁典，防止百姓遭受异端影响，防止局面发生惊天异变。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/940910/extras/0047570f1512ac4d93eaee4410db3625.avif?t=1751610521\" width=594 height=118 /></span><br><strong>重要亮点</strong><br>- 魔幻主题，剧情扣人心弦，灵感源自欧洲中世纪历史<br>- 同时采用2D美术和卡通渲染，视觉美术效果独特<br>- 动作操作流畅，行动之间，分毫之差决定胜负生死<br>- 攻势逼人，玩家可以同时利用剑招和技能击杀敌人<br>- 防御方式多样，例如翻滚躲闪和招架。<br>- 升级系统方便玩家调整角色实力，体验理想的游戏难度<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/940910/extras/de39db5a9ebf1ed5a9c6efd501749ab6.poster.avif?t=1751610521\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/940910/extras/de39db5a9ebf1ed5a9c6efd501749ab6.webm?t=1751610521\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/940910/extras/de39db5a9ebf1ed5a9c6efd501749ab6.mp4?t=1751610521\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/940910/extras/50a9e0832a4774e57041890b31324c30.avif?t=1751610521\" width=594 height=118 /></span><br><strong>开发团队寄语</strong><br>大家好！我是《米诺利亚》的制作人和监制rdein。<br>首先，正式宣布《米诺利亚》即将上线，我特别高兴，想把这份喜悦也分享给大家。这个游戏宇宙，从人物设定一直到最后，我都花了很多心血。游戏开发的过程中，我们不断探索和拓展这个宇宙中的各种概念，我觉得非常有意思。<br>这么多年来，这次是我第一次在新的宇宙里创作游戏，有一种焕然一新的感觉。虽然这么说，《米诺利亚》和我之前的项目确实有一些相似之处，尤其是《莫莫多拉》系列的最后一部作品《月下遐想》。<br>我们为《米诺利亚》付出了很多，我很自豪，希望大家喜欢这次奉上的故事和角色！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/940910/extras/45f39f43a474ef57d9aa7a7e891b6f3c.poster.avif?t=1751610521\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/940910/extras/45f39f43a474ef57d9aa7a7e891b6f3c.webm?t=1751610521\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/940910/extras/45f39f43a474ef57d9aa7a7e891b6f3c.mp4?t=1751610521\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/940910/extras/b111340302db5498b88eb806b090ab20.avif?t=1751610521\" width=594 height=118 /></span><br><strong>发行团队寄语</strong><br>大家好，我是Dangen Entertainment的Dan。我们之前就看到了《米诺利亚》的巨大魅力，所以耐着性子等待官宣的日子特别煎熬。这款游戏集合了《莫莫多拉》各部作品的亮点和长处，同时增加剧情方面的笔墨，讲述了一个肃穆的故事。我特别欣赏Bombservice这次采用的视觉风格，这次尝试十分特别，既保证了美术效果，又延续了开发团队在前几部作品中不断超越自我的出色表现。 <br><br>这部游戏不同凡响，如果你和我一样喜欢平台动作游戏，这款游戏绝对不能错过！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/940910/extras/ea60582b92d708b180315a03441a18a6.poster.avif?t=1751610521\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/940910/extras/ea60582b92d708b180315a03441a18a6.webm?t=1751610521\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/940910/extras/ea60582b92d708b180315a03441a18a6.mp4?t=1751610521\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
